Title: On the Elegies and the Sonnets
---
The Elegies and The Sonnets support each other reciprocally, and I see it
as an endless blessing that I, with the same breath, was able to fill both
sailsï¼š the small, rust-colored sail of the sonnets and the great white
canvas of the Elegies.
